title: Alex Jones Show - 2011 Aug 09 TU [sebaygo1]

The Alex Jones Show
Tuesday, 09 August 2011


[sebaygo1]


Scheduled Guests
................

From the Infowars web site ::

Alex talks with PrisonPlanet.com editors and journalists Paul Joseph Watson and Steve Watson about the riots spreading across Britain. 

Alex also talks with Stewart Rhodes of the Oath Keepers about Quartzite, Arizona, Chief of Police Jeff Gilbert calling the Oath Keepers, the Greater Phoenix Tea Party, and the Sons of Liberty Riders "terrorists" during a public meeting. 

Marc Morano, who runs the climate website ClimateDepot.com for the Committee for a Constructive Tomorrow, talks with Alex about Al Gore losing it and cursing out skeptics of the climate scam at the globalist Aspen Institute in Colorado earlier this month.

Today's broadcast went 5 minutes into a 4th hour.
